OL,3,CArsonist who murdered young family in
OL,4,Cflat fire has jail sentenced reduced
OL,6,FAn arsonist who murdered a mother and
OL,7,Fher two young daughters by pouring
OL,8,Fpetrol through the letterbox of their
OL,9,Fflat before torching their home, has
OL,10,Fwon his bid to reduce his jail time.
OL,12,FJamie Barrow, 32, was of Fatoumatta
OL,13,FHydara, 28, and her daughters, Fatimah
OL,14,Fand Naeemah Drammeh, aged three and
OL,15,Fone.
OL,17,FThe family died due to smoke
OL,18,Finhalation after Barrow set their home
OL,19,Fon fire.
