OL,3,CArsonist who murdered young family in
OL,4,Cflat fire has jail sentenced reduced
OL,6,FBarrow drank several cans of lager
OL,7,Fbefore taking petrol from his
OL,8,Fmotorbike and setting the home alight
OL,9,Fin November 2022.
OL,11,FProsecutors said Barrow had a
OL,12,F"grievance" with the family, over
OL,13,Frubbish being left in an alleyway.
OL,15,FHe then stood outside the home in
OL,16,FFairisle Close in Clifton to watch the
OL,17,Ffire - ignoring the screams of the
OL,18,Ffamily who were trapped inside.
