OL,3,CArsonist who murdered young family in
OL,4,Cflat fire has jail sentenced reduced
OL,6,FIn a ruling at the Royal Courts of
OL,7,FJustice in London on Tuesday, Lord
OL,8,FJustice Singh, Mr Justice Jay and
OL,9,FJudge Mayo lowered his sentence to 38
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FThey said the original sentence was
OL,13,F"manifestly excessive in the
OL,14,Fcircumstances of this case".
OL,16,FThe judges also expressed their
OL,17,F"sincere sympathy" to family members,
OL,18,Fadding: "Nothing in this judgment
OL,19,Fshould be taken in any way to detract
OL,20,Ffrom the gravity of the offences
OL,21,Fcommitted by this appellant."
